WEBVTT

00:01.690 --> 00:04.009
Kids, I'll never forget
the first time

00:04.011 --> 00:05.679
I told your mother I loved her.

00:05.681 --> 00:07.697
It was a rainy day in New York.

00:07.699 --> 00:09.049
<i>We just had a horrible lunch.</i>

00:09.051 --> 00:11.017
<i>The movie we wanted to see</i>
<i>was sold out,</i>

00:11.019 --> 00:12.102
<i>and I just looked at her</i>

00:12.104 --> 00:15.004
<i>and said, "I love you."</i>

00:15.006 --> 00:16.423
<i>It was a big deal for me.</i>

00:16.425 --> 00:19.025
<i>I hadn't said that</i>
<i>to a girl since...</i>

00:19.027 --> 00:20.811
I love you, Robin.

00:20.813 --> 00:23.363
I'm serious.

00:24.515 --> 00:27.317
Do you remember why we
broke up in the first place?

00:27.319 --> 00:28.618
We asked each other,
"Where do you want

00:28.620 --> 00:29.770
<i>to be in five years?"</i>

00:29.772 --> 00:32.989
<i>And our answers</i>
<i>were just too different.</i>

00:32.991 --> 00:34.357
Well, it's
five years later,

00:34.359 --> 00:37.544
and where are we?

00:37.546 --> 00:39.379
Standing on the roof

00:39.381 --> 00:42.198
<i>where I kissed you</i>
<i>for the first time.</i>

00:43.468 --> 00:46.303
I know this is
a lot to process,

00:46.305 --> 00:48.472
so no pressure here.

00:48.474 --> 00:52.058
Just... what do you think?

00:53.094 --> 00:54.544
You know what?
You're exhausted, it's late.

00:54.546 --> 00:55.545
Let's just go to sleep.

00:55.547 --> 00:56.713
Well, good night.

01:00.518 --> 01:01.985
<i>What the hell was that?</i>

01:01.987 --> 01:03.487
<i>Okay, I can fix this.</i>

01:03.489 --> 01:07.707
I-I was just temporarily insane
<i>because of my Lyme disease,</i>

01:07.709 --> 01:12.712
<i>which I got on a camping trip</i>
<i>that I didn't tell her about</i>

01:12.714 --> 01:17.751
<i>because... I go camping</i>
<i>in secret.</i>

01:17.753 --> 01:19.586
<i>Perfect.</i>

01:19.588 --> 01:21.671
<i>Or I could say, "I'm sorry,</i>
<i>we're great as friends.</i>

01:21.673 --> 01:23.290
<i>Let's just forget</i>
<i>I ever said anything."</i>

01:23.292 --> 01:24.291
<i>Yeah, that's probably better.</i>

01:24.293 --> 01:26.376
<i>Okay, here goes.</i>

01:29.246 --> 01:32.248
I go camping in secret.

